{"tid":2494426,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中华文化偉大復興  風景區立「媳婦餵婆婆喝奶」雕像","createTime":"2021-04-18T14:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T18:44:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"11aae17250d7474734bd94f6a305e48f14456a07","tid":2494426,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:48:05.000Z","msg":"綜合中媒報導，浙江湖州營盤山景區公園，近日被發現立了一座「媳婦給婆婆餵乳」雕像，看起來十分突兀，也與現代風俗民情十分不合。不少看到雕像的民眾，更直接向相關單位檢舉，要求園方改進。<br />\n<br />\n對此，園方工作人員指出，雕像是《二十四孝》中「乳姑不怠」的故事。「乳姑不怠」指唐代官員崔山南的曾祖母年紀大、牙齒脫落，不能吃米飯。崔的祖母十分孝順，每天梳洗後，就用自己的乳汁去餵養婆婆。<br />\n<br />\n工作人員還嗆聲，可能投訴的是年輕人，不知道中國祖孫相傳的《二十四孝》，也不懂得孝順。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/novelty/breakingnews/3503974\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fnovelty%2Fbreakingnews%2F3503974&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpruZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=45a2d745\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fnovelty%2Fbreakingnews%2F3503974&h=8452fd93\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/novelty/breakingnews/3503974</a>"},{"pid":"c5999613f2715a74420a35caae6797935a989b61","tid":2494426,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:50:46.000Z","msg":"愚孝"},{"pid":"b52eb3e9e87fc33a6072e930a0cdc3ca2532b1e8","tid":2494426,"uid":43809,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:38:21.000Z","msg":"餵埋老爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b681686ba1c1e17e692e6f890f6f3733c1a3e792","tid":2494426,"uid":258706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T17:58:37.000Z","msg":"個公園好成功咁利用個裝飾品做宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb785379220aa0e914ad6da5587b511ae77f11ad","tid":2494426,"uid":285559,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T18:12:28.000Z","msg":"二十四孝又玩人奶 又食屎 又人口販賣<br />\n淫審處應該要睇睇 封膠袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dea